column3: str

<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Mihsaja wishes to read the fate of a brave adventurer.
Gather spices to make chai tea.
Speak with Mihsaja.
You have a look in your eyes I am well familiar with. You wish to see the threads of fate which guide you, yes? What if I told you they could be illuminated through the fine art of reading chai tea?

Yes, the last remnant of a cup of tea can show your fate, the leaves and spices in the cup spelling out a message for those who can read it. This art has been perfected over generations in Thavnair, and I am willing to share it with you. Are you willing to take my gift?
Splendid! Before we begin, however, you must gather the spices we will use with your own hands. It's the only way to attune the tea to your destiny.
I have marked on your map a location where you can harvest three different spices. You will choose two of these, and do not make this choice lightly─it may very well decide the course of your future.
The fortune-teller wrote that the Thavnairian bay leaf improves the workings of the stomach, preventing discomfort and embarrassing irregularities in the gut.
Pick the Thavnairian bay leaf?
The fortune-teller wrote that the root of the singabera raises body temperature to expel toxins and other harmful substances from the body.
Pick the singabera root?
The fortune-teller wrote that the talisman needleleaf dispels negative thoughts, bringing a sense of calm to those who consume them.
Pick the talisman needleleaf?
You have returned with the spices, I see. You hold your future in your hands. Now, give them to me, and I shall brew a tea you are not soon to forget.
And here you are. This tea will decide your destiny, but that doesn't mean it cannot be delicious as well. I hope I don't have to convince you to drink until the final drop.
See? Delicious, yes? Now, pass the cup to me, and I will read your fate.
Ah, most curious. Fascinating...
There is a great revelation ahead of you. A revelation that involves the gods themselves. What will you learn? How will it change you? The tea does not say.

Oh, you will have an unexpected reunion with someone from your past. Will it be a lover, friend, family, or an erstwhile comrade-in-arms? The tea does not say, but it shall surely become a pivot on which your destiny turns.
Oh hoho, there is great wealth in store for you, but only if you make the right choices. Lay down your weapons and pick up a map and tools─the trade will be well worth it.

Well, how does it feel? A glimpse of foresight is often an enlightening experience, and I hope that my humble skills can dispel doubt in the days ahead. Thank you for giving me the chance to hone my craft further.
